  • Constructor Details

    • ChartDataset

      public ChartDataset(IonChamberDataset measuredDataset, int current, int margin)
      Create a new ChartDataset given the measured measuredDataset seriesData and initial current and margin.

      Note: The units for current are generally uA or nA, and it is up to the caller to ensure they match whatever was used when measuring.

      Parameters:
      measuredDataset - The ion chamber measured dose rate seriesData
      current - The initial current for the linearFit computation
      margin - The initial margin (percent) for the linearFit computation
